snippet.title: Entropy : Zero - Uprising - Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Step in the boots of a Civil Protection Unit trapped right in the middle of the Uprising in this modification for Entropy : Zero.

Our ModDB page:
https://www.moddb.com/mods/entropy-zero-uprising

Music by CW3D.

The mod is set to release on the ninth of April (date might vary, depending on timezones).
Thank you for sticking with us on this journey!
